Feature: CLI telemetry — local-only usage analytics lifecycle # scenarios/cli/cli_telemetry.feature:1
  Telemetry is opt-in and local-only. Data is stored in
  ~/.anklume/telemetry/ and never leaves the machine. These
  scenarios test the full telemetry lifecycle: enable, log,
  report, disable, clear.
  @requires.cli_help
  Scenario: Telemetry --help shows all 5 user commands                    # scenarios/cli/cli_telemetry.feature:10
    Given "python3" is available                                          # scenarios/steps/common_steps.py:12
