Feature: Doctor checks — system health verification # scenarios/generated/doctor_functional.feature:1
  Verify that the doctor diagnostic tool works correctly,
  detects available/missing tools, and produces useful output.
  @requires.doctor_syntax
  Scenario: doctor.sh runs without crashing             # scenarios/generated/doctor_functional.feature:6
    Given "bash" is available                           # scenarios/steps/common_steps.py:12
