Feature: Git push production protection # scenarios/generated/git_push_protection.feature:1
  As a sysadmin deploying anklume in production
  I want git push to be blocked on deployed instances
  So that production infrastructure is not accidentally modified
  Feature: Git push production protection  # scenarios/generated/git_push_protection.feature:1

  Scenario: Pre-push hook exists and is executable  # scenarios/generated/git_push_protection.feature:9
